pc|H5|nt|My choice of opening lead is a heart. Although my diamonds are a little stronger, I'd opt to lead the major... At least there will never be 5 hearts in dummy, while there might be 5 diamonds. From a weak 4- or 5-card suit, I prefer to lead second highest. That way, when I lead a small spot, partner can count on me for an honour. However, before you do so, you should discuss your leads with your partner.|pg||
nt|Declarer's plan:
